# 4. NEVER commit .env.local to the repository
#
# For production deployment:
# - Set ALPHA_VANTAGE_API_KEY in your hosting platform's environment variables
# - Examples: Vercel (Project Settings > Environment Variables)
#             AWS Lambda (Environment variables)
